title: GoPro Music: Live From Squaw Valley with Christine Donaldson - Done in One March Winner
description:
Christine Donaldson brings her musical talent to the slopes to win the Done In One contest for March, winning $1,000 dollars and music gear provided by Guitar Center.

Shot 100% on the HERO4® camera

Music
Christine Donaldson "Springtime Blues"
